{"tid":723304,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食評：元朗泗記+有得餃","createTime":"2018-06-30T09:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T12:26:36.000Z","uid":181719,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"00f311564a98b7c6dc1f73047ea68130a29e6bb3","tid":723304,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:34:15.000Z","msg":"早幾晚放工又去咗元朗搵食，行到去建業街，見泗記冇乜人，就入咗去食。之前佢做臘味，標榜係自製，已經好想去試，但成個冬天過埋都去唔成，呢晚去到，sor，已經冇臘味喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁咪死死地氣求其嗌個咸魚肉片飯算。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/172845_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F172845_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=80f6b3c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上檯時店員話餸喺碗底，咁咪食住面頭塊咸魚先。咸魚我一向鍾意實肉，呢度雖然係梅香嘅，但食落唔死咸唔腥，都OK，撈飯嘅豉油相比起黎就完全唔夠咸，可能食緊咸魚，直頭覺得啲豉油冇味添，不過啲飯蒸得幾好，顆粒分明。食到底啲肉片幾有鮮味，不過一樣略嫌淡口，我又唔記得影相，罪過罪過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n店員似乎幾hardsell啲湯，但我就冇乜興趣，飲兩杯依家越黎越少有嘅清茶好過，久違嘅茶記味道，35蚊就埋咗單。<br />\n<br />\n去食第二餐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n建業街係食街黎，兩邊馬路全部食肆，泗記隔離已經係之前介紹過嘅flavour kitchen，再行幾步就係有得餃喇，入去食碗餃當round 2，仲有世界盃睇添 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到好多客嗌麵食，都有啲心郁，但係上半場已經食咗個飯，食唔落啦，於是點咗8粒芹菜豬肉餃，估唔到淨餃唔只冇麵，係連湯都冇。食落餃皮略厚，餡料算足，不過芹香蓋過哂肉味喇，其中一兩隻仲食到有類似碎骨嘅異物，真係好一般 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/172914_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F172914_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=67be4807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/173339_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F173339_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=dc6c6dbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食食吓發現好多人叫醉雞翼，唔爭在叫埋，食淨打包啫。呢隻雞翼就全晚最佳表現喇，37蚊8隻，數量上已經好抵叫，諗住數量多即係好細隻？結果好大隻。諗住大隻即係唔入味？結果又好入味、好有酒香 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/172950_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F172950_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=98771f7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n埋單時睇到牆上剪報，原來呢間野仲投咗美食車黎做，真係估佢唔到。"},{"pid":"56d634bfbe6319c8325c217ed222c95f98126b57","tid":723304,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:35:12.000Z","msg":"影個餡張相調轉咗添 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a86a6e773bbef99fb25c16a53b2f37bf7e8edc","tid":723304,"uid":177272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:39:20.000Z","msg":"食過有得餃幾好食 係無咩位迫左啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"352de3a6deab4b9d448d78702389d845bc9d0278","tid":723304,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18a86a6e773bbef99fb25c16a53b2f37bf7e8edc","tid":723304,"uid":177272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:39:20.000Z","msg":"食過有得餃幾好食 係無咩位迫左啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:40:33.000Z","msg":"我見好多人食煎餃 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嗌完個芹菜餃即刻後悔"},{"pid":"28b075b7a58ca7b54ba09ef6c1c2ed581635188b","tid":723304,"uid":49176,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:51:42.000Z","msg":"好中意食有得餃<br />\n就係中意佢果種厚皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64fcfb7f3bba4acef865f894ba87a9f6496c37d9","tid":723304,"uid":119832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T10:07:10.000Z","msg":"食梁記唔好？"},{"pid":"baed6e231eb4f0eca43a146b147c0b88b30963fc","tid":723304,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28b075b7a58ca7b54ba09ef6c1c2ed581635188b","tid":723304,"uid":49176,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:51:42.000Z","msg":"好中意食有得餃<br />\n就係中意佢果種厚皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T10:25:05.000Z","msg":"竟然 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁佢啲餡其實都足料嘅<br />\n但有碎骨真係比較差 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e5634a947a50d8e4a64b84f26af017a05966a1","tid":723304,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64fcfb7f3bba4acef865f894ba87a9f6496c37d9","tid":723304,"uid":119832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T10:07:10.000Z","msg":"食梁記唔好？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T10:25:52.000Z","msg":"下次試下先<br />\n陳綺貞好熟元朗喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a297a796bbf01d9cb7d0454d86089357ea8318","tid":723304,"uid":119832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f7e5634a947a50d8e4a64b84f26af017a05966a1","tid":723304,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64fcfb7f3bba4acef865f894ba87a9f6496c37d9","tid":723304,"uid":119832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T10:07:10.000Z","msg":"食梁記唔好？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T10:25:52.000Z","msg":"下次試下先<br />\n陳綺貞好熟元朗喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T10:29:05.000Z","msg":"失覺曬 <img src=\"/assets/fac